FBIS3-8693 "dreeu049_k_94004" FBIS-EEU-94-049 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Mar 1994 CROATIA Poll Shows 39.8 Percent Oppose Confederation AU1103183494 AU1103183494 Article Type:BFN [Editorial Report] Zagreb GLOBUS in Serbo-Croatian on 10 March on pages 5 and 6 carries a report on the results of an opinion poll on the possible confederation between Croatia and Bosnia-Herzegovina. The report does not contain any information on when and how the poll was conducted. The results are expressed in percentages and summarized as follows: ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Will you vote in favor or against the confederation with Bosnia-Herzegovina? | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |In favor |39.1 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Against |39.8 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Do not know |21.1 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Will you take part in the referendum on the creation of the confederation be-| |tween Croatia and the Bosnia-Herzegovina confederation? | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Yes |66.1 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |No |17.9 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Do not know |13.8 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Do not want to say |2.2 | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |What should the nature of relations be between the Republic of Croatia an-| |d Bosnia-Herzegovina? | -----------------------------------------------------------